12 likes, 1 comments - thenikkirichshow on February 8, 2024: "@thenikkirichshow with @d.ham3

Watch this Saturday, Feb. 10 (8:00-9:00 PM, ET/PT) on the CBS Television Network, and streaming on Paramount+ (live for Paramount+ with SHOWTIME subscribers, or on demand on Pluto TV and CBS.com".
